# Root build context is used only by apps/agent-web (context = repo root so the
# Dockerfile can pull source from packages/agent-web-ui). Ship just those trees;
# everything else (k8s, terraform, nix, .git, build output) stays out of context.
*
!apps
!packages
!package.json
!bun.lock
!turbo.json

# Even within the whitelisted trees, never send dependency/build artifacts.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.cache
**/*.log
